                Most American traders hit the same wall early in {currentYear}: they sign up for a firm, pay the evaluation fee, and suddenly discover the trading platform is region-blocked for US IPs, or the firm abruptly stops serving the United States altogether.
              </p>
              <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6">
                The regulatory environment, overseen by the <a href="https://www.cftc.gov/LearnAndProtect/AdvisoriesAndArticles/fraudadv_forex.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC)</a>, has become increasingly hostile to unregulated retail CFDs. MetaQuotes’ aggressive ban on US traders using MetaTrader 4 (MT4) and MetaTrader 5 (MT5) through offshore unregulated firms caused mass industry panic. In {currentYear}, trading with an unverified, simulated-only shop is financial suicide.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-blue-600/5 border border-blue-500/20 p-6 rounded-2xl">
                <p class="text-slate-300 italic m-0 font-medium">
                  While competitors panicked, FXIFY proactively pivoted their infrastructure, ensuring 100% uninterrupted access for their US client base.
                </p>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section id="why-fxify" class="scroll-mt-32 mb-20">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">Why FXIFY is the #1 Choice for US Traders</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-400 mb-12">
                Here is exactly why FXIFY stands head and shoulders above the competition for the professional American trader today.
              </p>

              <div class="space-y-12">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs">1</span>
                    US-Compliant Trading Infrastructure (DXtrade & TradingView)
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">
                    When MetaQuotes cut off US access, FXIFY seamlessly transitioned its American clients to DXtrade (built by financial software giant <a href="https://dx.trade/prop-trading/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Devexperts</a>). This platform offers institutional-grade charting with native TradingView integration and flawless execution. By using this provider, FXIFY entirely bypassed the regulatory licensing hurdles that plagued older MT4/MT5 setups. Your access will never be arbitrarily cut off by software disputes.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Custom User Image -->
                <div class="my-12">
                  <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-2 border border-slate-800 shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <Image 
                      src={fxifyUSReport} 
                      alt="FXIFY US Compliant Platform Proof" 
                      width={800}
                      height={450}
                      class="rounded-xl w-full h-auto" 
                      loading="eager"
                      fetchpriority="high"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-center text-xs text-slate-500 mt-4 italic text-balance">Screenshot: The FXIFY dashboard featuring deep analytics [Verified {currentMonthName} {currentYear}].</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs">2</span>
                    Genuine Broker-Backing (FXPIG)
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">
