                  </p>
                  <div class="bg-slate-950 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 font-semibold mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-500">What this means for you:</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 m-0 leading-relaxed">
                      Your trades interact with genuine market liquidity. You benefit from raw spreads starting at 0.0 pips and true STP execution. This practically eliminates the artificial slippage commonly experienced during high-impact US news events like CPI releases or Non-Farm Payrolls.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs">3</span>
                    Tailored for the New York Session
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">Aggressive US session traders need flexible rules. FXIFY allows:</p>
                  <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none p-0 m-0">
                    <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 text-sm flex gap-3">
                      <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> <span>Expert Advisors (EAs) and Algorithmic Trading</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 text-sm flex gap-3">
                      <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> <span>Martingale and Grid Strategies</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 text-sm flex gap-3">
                      <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> <span>Holding positions over the weekend</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 text-sm flex gap-3">
                      <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold">✓</span> <span>Trading directly through high-impact news</span>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <p class="text-slate-400 mt-6 italic">Whether you are trading the NAS100, US30, or major dollar pairs, their servers are optimized to handle the extreme volatility of the NYSE open.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs">4</span>
                    First Payout On-Demand & Up to 90% Splits
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">
                    FXIFY offers an industry-leading <strong>First Payout On-Demand</strong> feature. Instead of waiting for a rigid 14-day or 30-day cycle, US traders can request their first payout immediately after closing their first profitable funded trade. Coupled with profit splits that scale up to 90% and account scaling up to $4,000,000, the financial upside is massive.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs">5</span>
                    Instant Funding Options for {currentYear}
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-400">
                    Don't want to pass a multi-phase challenge? In {currentYear}, FXIFY expanded its offerings to include <strong>Instant Funding Lite</strong> (similar to <a href="/prop-firms/dna-funded" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">DNA Funded's instant models</a>) and <strong>Instant Funding Standard</strong>. You can bypass the evaluation entirely and start earning a profit split from day one.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section id="payouts" class="scroll-mt-32 mb-20">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">Funding & Payouts: Local US Logistics</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8">Traditional banking in the United States can present major hurdles when dealing with international prop firms due to strict KYC regulations enforced by entities like the <a href="https://www.nfa.futures.org/members/member-resources/files/regulatory-guide-forex-transactions.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">National Futures Association (NFA)</a>. FXIFY has completely streamlined this financial plumbing specifically for their American client base.</p>
              
