                  <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-3">Crypto Payouts (The Industry Standard)</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">The fastest, most reliable method for US traders to receive their profit splits in {currentYear} is via cryptocurrency. By withdrawing via stablecoins (USDT/USDC) or major coins like Bitcoin, you bypass slow domestic wire transfers. Your USD profits hit your wallet in under 24 hours.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
