                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Purchasing your initial 1-Phase, 2-Phase, or Instant Funding evaluation is frictionless. You can buy in instantly using any major US-issued Visa or Mastercard through their encrypted payment gateways.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-8 bg-green-500/5 border border-green-500/20 p-4 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-4">
                <span class="text-green-500 text-xl">💵</span>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 font-medium m-0"><strong>100% Refundable Fees:</strong> Pass the evaluation, and your initial challenge fee is refunded to you with your first payout.</p>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section id="broker-backed" class="scroll-mt-32 mb-20">
