              <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6">The CFTC actively targets and shuts down unregulated offshore entities operating as unregistered dealers. Because FXIFY utilizes a true broker-backed model through FXPIG, they possess the actual capital reserves necessary to pay out six-figure profit splits.</p>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                With over $40 million paid out to a network of active users globally, you are choosing a firm that relies on real market hedging and robust liquidity—not just the losses of failed challengers—to pay its funded traders.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section id="faq" class="scroll-mt-32 mb-20">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-slate-950 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800">
